Package freemarker.core

Interface TemplateProcessingTracer.TracedElement

Enclosing interface:
TemplateProcessingTracer
public static interface TemplateProcessingTracer.TracedElement
Information about the template element that we enter of exit; do NOT implement this (outside FreeMarker), as new methods can be added to this anytime!
Since:
2.3.33
